The paper discusses the development of question answering systems, which involves natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning (ML) techniques. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) are also relevant as they deal with ML and NLP. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible sub-category as it deals with the development of ML algorithms. Finally, cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a less likely sub-category, but it could be relevant as the paper discusses the development process of QA systems.
